As soon as I got to know that Paradise started serving Haleem at their various outlets, I had to rush to try it.

First things first, from temperature checks to sanitizing to social distancing to contactless dining and delivery, they are following all the norms. 

Being a renowned brand, Paradise is synonymous with TRUST and they emphasise on Stringent cleanliness, hygiene & safety at all stages of Operation. 

Paradise also has their own online delivery app, which is available on both playstore & iOS. The app is totally user friendly and easy to use and has some great offers.

latestIgtvVideos.title: My 7 steps morning skin care routine - acne prone skin ☀️🦋
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
My skin care routine is one of the most requested video ever! 💁‍♀️💦 I’ve been postponing since forever because I never stick to one routine. I keep changing the products every now and then because I feel my skin weird and it’s not the same all the time! So currently I’m following this routine that I showed in the video! Super simple 7 step morning skincare 🦋💛 I strongly believe when you include facial massage techniques in your skin care game, it really helps in blood circulation and give that plum & glowyy skin! 🌟🌟 Also I’ve invested on a lot of luxury skin care products but I should say I was disappointed for shredding money on them. Not all products work on your skin even if you spend a lot ( common misconception) Skin care is all about trial and error for me! I’ve had few drug store products cause severe skin damage as well. So please be mindful when you’re picking your skincare products! 💕🌻 Details :
* Cleaner : deep cleanser by @neutrogena , works as a scrub too. 💃Can be used everyday! Very mild. * Facial mist : my all time favorite @forestessentials facial mist 💦💦
* Toner : @plumgoodness green tea alcohol free toner 🍵 💚
* Moisturizer : @kamaayurveda Eladi hydrating face cream * Sunblock : advices by dermatologist @lashieldofficial spf 50 ☀️☀️
* Lip balm : @maybelline , fav been using it for almost 7 years now! 🌝💗
* Jade roller @isleofskin for facial massage 🧿 .

latestIgtvVideos.title: DIY SCRUNCHIE 💕🌸⚡️☀️
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hey guys! Let’s bring out our creative skills and stay stylish during quarantine! 
Since we cannot buy new stuff right now, let’s make something on our own! I absolutely love scrunchies, they’re super easy to style and always trendy! Replace your normal hair tie with your own diy scrunchie 💜 make a sustainable move! 
All you need : - Old cloth or any cloth that’s not being used - Sewing kit 🧵 - Hair tie - Scissors ✂️ Watch the video for the process 😉 I’ve used a plain pink cotton fabric, you can use any printed, old cloth, lehenga mater or anything that’s available! 
P.s - Sorry for the bad camera angle, I had to self film it 🤓 
#Srunchies #DIY #QuarantineDairies #SustainableFashion
